<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-6C36E002-6A5D-48DD-B710-AC947166C459" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-6C36E002-6A5D-48DD-B710-AC947166C459" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">05 How to Install the printhead carriage unit)</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-0E3E2CA2-5349-4FAF-80F5-347AA9765351"><p class="- topic/p ">This document describes the installation of the Printhead carriage unit. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_CEA4CD427612471CA3540AD5430B21C2" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_B007BBFF5E5743C89A24651737F64808" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Screwdriver Torx T25
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">3 needles.
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> 5 cable ties.
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Y-coarse adjustment tool for adjusting Tissue Wipe cassette maintenance unit. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Adjustment tool 2,5mm (2x)
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-2D7D94A0-B26C-4C0B-B6A3-20C8621663A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-F2BD1CD8-D885-4A5A-B5AE-580392833C42" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CE352008-6065-43E2-A983-38B892D6D0D6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CE352008-6065-43E2-A983-38B892D6D0D6-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_83EFA574E57B4B64A0DD595529E957E2" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to Install</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Hook in the new printhead carriage unit above the cut-away locations in the guide rail.
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-98857965-F159-49D5-A038-CAA0FF726BE1" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Ensure that the ruler is undamaged as you perform this task, and confirm that it is positioned accurately in the middle of the sensor and correctly aligned with the center of the guidance.
</p></note><note id="GUID-660C2496-DD4C-42B8-9959-96ADEE0DDA79" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not install the printheads yet
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-30311B37-36E9-4CA4-8D6D-582B4B70A909" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CE352008-6065-43E2-A983-38B892D6D0D6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CE352008-6065-43E2-A983-38B892D6D0D6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The following items have to be transferred from the replaced unit to the new print head carriage unit:
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Guidance cleaners
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Aerosol ink filter units
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mirror box Left and Right
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">M&amp;C-unit
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Carriage PBA assembly
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cover (incl manifolds) of the carriage unit
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Printheads
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Clamp bracket (print heads)
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Plate shielding
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">Cover (incl manifolds) of the carriage unit
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the guidance cleaners.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">See: 
<xref keyref="05DISA008" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-90671113-E055-4561-9EEF-14CD9B5A386A.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05 How to remove the Guidance cleaners (felt)?>05 How to remove the Guidance cleaners (felt)</xref>
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the ‘How to Install’ part of the instruction.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the drive belt of the printhead carriage. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">See: 
<xref keyref="05DISA009" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-897E944B-74E6-4F78-82E2-F9C042C1C99C.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05 How to remove the printhead carriage drive belt?>05 How to remove the printhead carriage drive belt</xref>
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the ‘How to Install’ part of the instruction.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install Aerosol Ink Filter Unit at the Right hand side.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Install the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Put the T-joint downward in the slit of the hotbox. 
</p><fig id="GUID-27EFC2AD-A2A5-4DAF-8649-C118DBF81D42" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0E3D00E2-CA7B-4C24-8FFA-2D014040FF14-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0E3D00E2-CA7B-4C24-8FFA-2D014040FF14-low.png"/></fig></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1F3AA524-EE7D-42C9-AF59-E0E61AE3026D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C5919F60-72E0-4094-949E-AB6954CF08AF-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C5919F60-72E0-4094-949E-AB6954CF08AF-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Aerosol Ink Filter Unit (Right hand side). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-74968692-BDA8-4C58-8F40-E70832D05E42" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install the mirror box.
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes.
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Push bracket lock downwards to secure the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit in vertical direction. 
</p></li></ol><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Fix the bracket lock
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-A329C9FE-8FC7-411A-B870-58C461503B5B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CAEB71FE-59C5-4FFA-9B35-C04339730958-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CAEB71FE-59C5-4FFA-9B35-C04339730958-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fix the bracket lock 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Fasten the screw (T M3x8B). 
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-88B8943B-2E53-42E3-8A06-4AA57D07E2E8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EE7B3017-84D0-42D0-8E84-812A231184F2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EE7B3017-84D0-42D0-8E84-812A231184F2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Connect the harness of the fan. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-350C5601-4896-4626-9BF5-7AC17D515D59" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-449C1283-18EB-46AF-ABC6-C42096C99F01-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-449C1283-18EB-46AF-ABC6-C42096C99F01-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install Aerosol Ink Filter Unit (Left hand side)
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-5E0115E7-D51E-4285-AF19-15EF32A8FD3A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E6F792CF-711D-4AC2-B9E7-6DD2B40631C4-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E6F792CF-711D-4AC2-B9E7-6DD2B40631C4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Put the T-joint downward in the slit of the hotbox. 
</p><fig id="GUID-46B9D7EC-8981-415D-A07A-1D6DCCE7A982" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1880557F-DB1C-46A0-BA1A-C7740940C7A0-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1880557F-DB1C-46A0-BA1A-C7740940C7A0-low.png"/></fig></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EB89D875-AA2D-47C8-BDC8-58545529CD33" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F548B183-4F51-4D35-BCB0-1EEFCEED1544-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F548B183-4F51-4D35-BCB0-1EEFCEED1544-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After positioning of the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit, the free distance in the slit of the hotbox is nominal 4mm. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The positioning, equal to the unit on the RIGHT-hand side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D66D6B59-1227-41BB-8C9C-1174F0CEFD1E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E845A23-EC84-4839-9C58-1A691228CB9D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the mirror box. 
</p><note id="GUID-474675FB-8B61-43D9-81FE-3EEA075669C0" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Route the ink hose with the green cable tie below the hot box. 
</p></note><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the 4 screws that are accessible through the 4 holes. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Mount clip. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-63DEFDD0-0C64-4EB3-977E-2A68C8728BFD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0FAC73DC-040F-4177-B0FE-343DB0D62EC6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0FAC73DC-040F-4177-B0FE-343DB0D62EC6-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-9E85D1D0-6689-4028-AA14-C582E01CFBE1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1D3B791E-CF46-4A63-9A0F-9ED18D996DC3-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1D3B791E-CF46-4A63-9A0F-9ED18D996DC3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Fixate the ink hoses to the mirror box with 3 cable ties. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the cable ties.
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B44F17E6-851C-4AA1-92B2-2B1C4CB1EE9F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-214A15F5-B448-4F32-BB57-99102F87DB76-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-214A15F5-B448-4F32-BB57-99102F87DB76-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install the bracket lock to secure the Aerosol Ink Filter Unit.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EBD60954-71B0-41C7-9B3F-2C205BE75D57" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-50187DA4-CF00-420E-8FD7-67F3551EE078-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-50187DA4-CF00-420E-8FD7-67F3551EE078-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fix the bracket lock. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Fasten the screw (T M3x8B). 
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-050C7507-D9C3-4C32-BE10-13CB0770BB45" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EEBF552D-C541-49F1-BDA3-EC8839335A3E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EEBF552D-C541-49F1-BDA3-EC8839335A3E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">17
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Connect the harness of the fan.
</p><note id="GUID-1C9945A9-2937-4F62-B34D-4F060A339B9F" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Double check all 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">air / ink tube connections</b>.
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FE6EFCAD-32ED-4922-A474-D2E98E6A56A3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33924CCF-3526-4170-88F7-CDF394510DDD-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33924CCF-3526-4170-88F7-CDF394510DDD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">18
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the ink tubes with 2 cable ties to the frame.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-945A91CD-D5D9-4758-8BAB-6F58E41482A3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0C681FDE-5E95-4E03-A345-B55A3292489B-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0C681FDE-5E95-4E03-A345-B55A3292489B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">19
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install the Carriage PBA-assembly.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B5658D1D-B111-43BA-BCEC-0C1542739A0C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-41FC4F76-CB3B-4269-BC2E-240BEFFE5E3C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-41FC4F76-CB3B-4269-BC2E-240BEFFE5E3C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">20
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Connect the flat cables, air and ink tubes to the printhead carriage (2 screws).
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C1A88871-756C-4BB5-A21A-E7631F6821EA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EA8C69AB-2301-4836-9CE5-CE4F6BCEC894-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EA8C69AB-2301-4836-9CE5-CE4F6BCEC894-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">21
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Guide the air tube and optical fiber cable through the frame of the printhead carriage.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Attach optical fiber cable and air tube to Carrier frame with cable tie.
